REFERRED TO CONSUMER AFFAIRS AND PROTECTION

Title: Relates to online marketplace verification
Summary: Requires all online marketplaces to require every person engaged in a transaction on its marketplace website, application or software, to verify their identity with the online marketplace.
LawCode: Add ยง396-ddd, Gen Bus L
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the general business law, in relation to online marketplace verification
